OL,3,CWhy is the newly elected Speaker of
OL,4,Cthe House of Commons dragged into
OL,5,Cposition?
OL,7,FSir Lindsay Hoyle has been re-elected
OL,8,Fas Speaker of the House of Commons and
OL,9,Fwas led back to his position with some
OL,10,Fhelp.
OL,12,FIt is all change in Westminster this
OL,13,Fweek, as 335 MPs are taking office for
OL,14,Fthe first time - the largest number of
OL,15,Fnew faces since 1945.
OL,17,FBut despite a new government and new
OL,18,FMPs, some traditions in the House of
OL,19,FCommons will remain the same.
