OL,3,CWhy is the newly elected Speaker of
OL,4,Cthe House of Commons dragged into
OL,5,Cposition?
OL,7,FIn Canada, Greg Fergus became the
OL,8,Flatest speaker to be dragged to the
OL,9,Fchair in 2023 by Prime Minister Justin
OL,10,FTrudeau and Leader of the Opposition
OL,11,FPierre Poilievre.
OL,13,FIn New Zealand, also in 2023, Gerry
OL,14,FBrownlee was accompanied into his new
OL,15,Fposition.
OL,17,FWhile in Australia Andrew Wallace
OL,18,Funderwent a similar procedure in 2021
OL,19,Fas he became Speaker of the House of
OL,20,FRepresentatives in Federal Parliament.
